metadata.name: Immerse yourself #1
metadata.description:
Immerse yourself is part of a series shot during sunrise in summer 2016. I the first serie I have ever shot and the idea was to portray woman in a more ethereal way. This is a mixture of animation and photography. 

1068× 1600 * 41,3MB

Paula Latimori is a photographer and filmmaker whose work explores photography through colors, textures and emotion.

Her work aims to blur the lines between a story where fantasy enters with a simple and natural point of view.

Her personal projects usually mix a very creative and artistic perspective with a very fresh and modern eye.
